{"tid":1431612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海港城個活動被取消係因為俾人抹黑，非常可惜","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:12:06.000Z","uid":265443,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"defdb0642d530986a3868d76d033fb9b64e55796","tid":1431612,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"由始至終都冇人話要做d咩過火嘅事，係邊個話去左就會亂？唔試做過又點知成效會如何？<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你地話琴日激光show搞到太空館？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU0DRnR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU0DRnR.jpg&h=cb859b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇警察嘅地方就唔會亂，商場貼告亦話唔歡迎警察，我地更加要去<br />\n我地只係去返一個可以去嘅地方，做返可以做嘅事，<br />\n因為海港城係香港人嘅商場<br />\n<br />\n去海港城同五大訴求有咩關係？<br />\n唔好俾商家再做旁觀者角色，逼佢地表態，究竟係企香港人個邊，定利益個邊<br />\n<br />\n無端端去搞人，人當我地係暴民，又俾對家有位入<br />\n搞手有冇講過要去打爛玻璃搶野？歎商場冷氣你地不嬲都做開嫁啦只不過今次係人多少少啫<br />\n<br />\n點解針對海港城？成個香港紅底商場大把啦<br />\n唔係針對海港城，只不過佢係第一彈，搞手都講得好清楚<br />\n<br />\n重申，兄弟爬山，各有各做，你唔同意就阻止人去做去試，係非常唔健康嘅一個風氣<br />\n<br />\n結果就係有一個籌組左，已經放入抗爭日程嘅行動胎死腹中<br />\n<br />\n以上係我立場，下面希望有多d人良性討論，唔好淨係負評，唔該曬"},{"pid":"53ae83d56644af3fd8e47c99ed05fe4ff08f7037","tid":1431612,"uid":65790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"去海港城做咩<br />\n第一彈去新城市搞我支持"},{"pid":"98eb7b384296561d6e874f16121bdbc7b0b12934","tid":1431612,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"53ae83d56644af3fd8e47c99ed05fe4ff08f7037","tid":1431612,"uid":65790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"去海港城做咩<br />\n第一彈去新城市搞我支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解搞手要取消成件事"},{"pid":"342714cc6125428a84f9a73a64f3e9a1871a7298","tid":1431612,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"太溫和啦香港人"},{"pid":"78ab38c25ab8e7be8435cc59bcca0bcc9a24a12b","tid":1431612,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d30d3ad647f276872f1b508a4cda16e873aa21e","tid":1431612,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"救救劉細良<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431682\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1c9abc1b964c084408fa99662f211f0db676126b","tid":1431612,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"唔係遇然<br />\n<br />\n以昨晚粉嶺集會分析，對家現時策略：就算和理非集會，都瘋傳有打鬥，警方叫超大範圍商場拉閘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"beaccb81054e230af120147329cf4695c5a827e8","tid":1431612,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9abc1b964c084408fa99662f211f0db676126b","tid":1431612,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"唔係遇然<br />\n<br />\n以昨晚粉嶺集會分析，對家現時策略：就算和理非集會，都瘋傳有打鬥，警方叫超大範圍商場拉閘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:15:24.000Z","msg":"一定有人作怪，連登依加吹個風非常奇怪"},{"pid":"e8e3874a95d41b6e34d642cc8fad61df8c05e30d","tid":1431612,"uid":294073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"人未到，商場已經如臨大敵咁啦，旗都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p8wLwAg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp8wLwAg.png&h=14e4f295&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"779d62e65b97ddca1c6f7319f7007b5ad680d2ce","tid":1431612,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8e3874a95d41b6e34d642cc8fad61df8c05e30d","tid":1431612,"uid":294073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"人未到，商場已經如臨大敵咁啦，旗都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p8wLwAg